                                        <locus from="1" to="1" scheme="folios"/> leaf damaged and torn, glued to a modern paper support. Debris found in the gutter in many places, on <locus from="7r" to="7r" scheme="folios"/> even some plant matter. <locus from="S249r" to="S249r" scheme="folios"/>: offprint from facing page. Small stains and smudges throughout. On many leaves throughout the manuscript the ink has blead through the leaf with occasional loss of legibility, e.g. <locus from="221" to="221" scheme="folios"/>.</condition>
